SUMMARY:Yoga In Nature™\, ALL LEVELS\, Lake Crabtree Community Park
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\n**SPRING IS ALMOST HERE\, so join Yoga
  In Nature ™** as we do an **ALL LEVELS** vinyasa flow to yin yoga pract
 ice\, at this beautiful location\, facing the lake. Modifications provided
 . **Beginners welcome**. Connect with nature with all of your senses to fi
 nd calm and peace within as we practice yoga. Yoga heals. Nature heals. Yo
 ga In Nature.\n**Note that location is NOT in the gravel parking lot\, but
  in the open field:)**\n\nBRING YOUR OWN YOGA MAT\, towel\, water bottle\,
  and block (if you use one)\, sunscreen\, insect repellent (seasonal). You
  may also want to bring an old towel or liner for under your mat\, if the 
 ground is wet. We will meet in the open field area near the parking lot. $
 15/person Accepting Venmo @Darlene-Genander or PayPal dgenander@yogainnatu
 re.com or Zelle or cash\n\nLake Crabtree County Park\, past the entrance b
 ooth\, at the open field\, near volleyball courts and Old Beech Nature Tra
 il... first right after you enter the park.(If you get to the entrance whe
 re there are boat rentals and launch area you've gone too far).\nLake Crab
 tree County Park\, 1400 Aviation Parkway\, Morrisville
